			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>ReTargeter</strong> is currently looking for rockstar candidates to support and train under our Director of &nbsp;Inside Sales.</p>
<p>
Join <strong>ReTargeter</strong> for the opportunity to advance your career as part of a driven and passionate team. Your skill in building long-term relationships and dedication to client success will make your contributions invaluable. Grow as a key member of our team and become an expert in the advertising and media agency landscape. We value employee development and welcome those who are lifelong learners.</p>
<p>
In addition to a beautiful office in downtown SOMA, some of the perks include a fully stocked kitchen, daily catered lunches, a flexible vacation policy, a health care stipend, awesome co-workers, team events such as cooking classes and go-kart racing, birthday celebrations, and quarterly dinners with the CEO.</p>
<p>
<u><strong> Duties and Responsibilities: </strong></u></p>
<p>
Help the Director of Inside Sales and Account Executive team with initial outreach to high-level prospects. The Inside Sales Rep is a scout for the next big partnership, discovering key paths for ReTargeter to grow and expand our business.  Track communications with customers and prospects in Salesforce.  Answer customers&rsquo; basic product questions.  Capture lead metrics and customer trends. Present periodic proposals with your feedback on how to improve the sales process.</p>
<p>
Serve as an integral part of the ReTargeter team and help take the company to the next level.</p>
<p>
<u><strong> Requirements: </strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>
You have at least 1 year of sales experience, preferably in display, but not required.</li>
<li>
You are passionate about sales and determined to succeed.</li>
<li>
Your development plan includes everything from leading your own sales team to owning your own vertical.</li>
<li>
You are metrics driven and goal oriented.</li>
<li>
You enjoy having a sales goal while also being able to&nbsp; work with other team members on sales process, prospecting and training.</li>
<li>
You have a Bachelor&#39;s degree</li>
</ul>
<p>
This role has a base salary of 50K as well as commission, OTE is based on performance.</p>
<p>
<strong><u>You live by these values</u></strong></p>
<ul>
